For instance, in my starting page (I use PHP as server side language), I set an Angular constant like this: <script>
    angular.module("app").constant("CSRF_TOKEN", '<?=$csrf_token;?>'); 
</script>

Example of a service: 
mod.factory("CacheService", function($cacheFactory) { return { data:{ scrollY: 0 } }; });
then in controller: $scope.service = CacheService.data
